0new%20textbooks%20for%20primary%20and%20secondary%20students%20have%20several%20changes%2C%20The%20Daily%20Star%20newspaper%20said.%20The%20textbooks%20also%20removed%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BFather%20of%20the%20Nation%26quot%3B%20for%20Mujibur%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20textbooks%20for%20the%202025%20academic%20year%20will%20state%20that%20%26quot%3Bon%20March%2026%2C%201971%2C%20Ziaur%20Rahman%20declared%20the%20independence%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20on%20March%2027%2C%20he%20made%20another%20declaration%20of%20independence%20on%20behalf%20of%20Bangabandhu%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20quoted%20Prof%20AKM%20Reazul%20Hassan%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Curriculum%20and%20Textbook%20Board%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20has%20been%20included%20in%20the%20free%20textbooks%20where%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20declaration%20was%20mentioned%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20writer%20and%20researcher%20Rakhal%20Raha%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20making%20changes%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%20said%20they%20tried%20to%20free%20the%20textbooks%20from%20%26quot%3Bexaggerated%2C%20imposed%20history%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20revised%20the%20textbooks%20found%20that%20it%20wasn't%20fact-based%20information%20that%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20sent%20the%20wireless%20message%20%5Bdeclaring%20independence%5D%20while%20being%20arrested%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20army%2C%20and%20so%20they%20decided%20to%20remove%20it.%26quot%3B%20Earlier%2C%20in%20the%20textbooks%20of%20classes%20one%20to%2010%2C%20the%20information%20on%20who%20made%20the%20Declaration%20of%20Independence%20was%20changed%20according%20to%20the%20government%20in%20power%2C%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20widely%20believed%20among%20supporters%20of%20Awami%20League%20that%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20had%20made%20the%20announcement%20and%20that%20Ziaur%20Rahman%2C%20w