nvestigating%20terrorism%20links%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20vehicle%20contained%20a%20large%20explosive%20device.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Ftesla-cybertruck-linked-to-suspected-terror-attack-in-the-us-elon-musk-says-wrong-vehicle-%2Farticleshow%2F116883770.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20H-1B%20Visa%2C%20Trump%2C%20And%20The%20MAGA%20Backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidential%20inauguration%20on%20January%2020%2C%20an%20open%20battle%20has%20erupted%20between%20two%20groups%20of%20Trump%20supporters%20-%20DOGE%20(the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency)%20versus%20MAGA%20(Make%20America%20Great%20Again)%20-%20over%20the%20misuse%20of%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20programme%20by%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Trump%20seems%20to%20be%20supporting%20the%20DOGE%20team%20under%20tech%20titans%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20in%20the%20row%20over%20the%20visa%20programme%20that%20brings%20skilled%20workers%20to%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20Tesla%20CEO%20Musk%20admitted%20that%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20system%20was%20%26quot%3Bbroken%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20needed%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20reform%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-need-smart-people-trump-sides-with-elon-musk-on-h-1b-visa-row-7375202%5C%22%3ETrump%20chose%20to%20walk%20into%20the%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reportedly%20said%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Balways%20liked%26quot%3B%20H-1B%20visas%20and%20hired%20guest%20workers%20under%20the%20scheme%20-%20even%20though%20he%20has%20previously%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20programme.%20That%20has%20left%20his%20MAGA%20fan%20base%20in%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20resentment%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20became%20intense%20after%20the%20nomination%20of%20Sriram%20Krishnan%2C%20an%20Indian-origin%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20to%20lead%20AI%20policy%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20Krishnan's%20views%20on%20social%20media%20in%20the%20past%2C%20advocating%20relaxation%20in%20green%20card%20restrictions%20for%20skilled%20workers%2C%20have%20enraged%20MAGA%20critics%20who%20accuse%20him%20of%20pushing%20an%20%26quot%3BIndia%20First%26quot%3B%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20influencer%20Laura%20Loomer%20criticised%20Krishnan's%20appointment%20and%20blamed%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20for%20neglecting%20American%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20pitched%20Trump's%20advisors%20from%20the%20tech%20world%2C%20immigrants%20themselves%2C%20against%20native%20Republicans%20-%20the%20MAGA%20supporters.%20The%20MAGA%20group%20supported%20Trump%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20he%20will%20take%20strict%20action%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20immigration.%20Trump%20is%20known%20to%20have%20opposed%20H-1B%20visas%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20openly%20coming%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20H1B%20visa%20programme%20means%20that%20he%20is%20antagonising%20the%20hard-line%20anti-immigration%20supporters%20in%20the%20MAGA%20coalition%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Uma%20Purushothaman%2C%20Associate%20Professor%2C%20US%20Studies%2C%20School%20of%20International%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20given%20the%20strength%20of%20his%20victory%20this%20time%20and%20his%20close%20ties%20to%20techno%20oligarchs%20like%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20it%20is%20a%20constituency%20he%20might%20be%20willing%20to%20sideline%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20to%20the%20world%20that%20both%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20believe%20that%20America's%20tech%20industry%20relies%20heavily%20on%20engineers%20and%20professionals%20from%20countries%20like%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20your%20team%20to%20win%20the%20championship%2C%20you%20need%20to%20recruit%20top%20talent%20wherever%20they%20may%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20shortage%20of%20excellent%20engineering%20talent%26quot%3B%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'America%20beckons%2C%20but%20Americans%20repel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chasm%20between%20the%20old%20timers%20in%20the%20Trump%20camp%2C%20mostly%20far-right%20nativists%2C%20and%20the%20newcomers%20who%20came%20to%20America%20late%20as%20immigrants%20but%20are%20Trump%20supporters%20like%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%2C%20is%20now%20out%20in%20the%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikki%20Haley%2C%20Trump's%20former%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20a%20former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20is%20another%20major%20voice%20arguing%20against%20Ramaswamy%20and%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%2C%20like%20Ramaswamy%2C%20was%20born%20to%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20but%20joined%20the%20camp%20opposing%20the%20visa%20programme%20led%20by%20right-wing%20MAGA%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20faces%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20tightrope%20act%20as%20he%20prepares%20for%20his%20second%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20businessman%2C%20Trump%20knows%20the%20advantages%20of%20these%20programmes.%20Trump's%20stance%20means%20that%20his%20focus%20is%20going%20to%20be%20more%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20than%20shutting%20down%20visa%20programmes.%20He%20would%20possibly%20try%20to%20reform%20these%20programmes%2C%20though%2C%20as%20Musk%20has%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Purushothaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'America%20beckons%2C%20but%20Americans%20repel'%20is%20an%20old%20immigrant%20proverb%20born%20in%20the%20nineteenth%20century.%20Yet%20it%20holds%20true%20even%20today%20as%20native-born%20Republicans%2C%20some%20only%20a%20generation%20or%20two%20or%20more%20themselves%2C%20voice%20their%20resentment%20for%20new%20immigrants%20like%20Musk%2C%20Ramaswamy%20and%20Krishnan%20and%20their%20ilk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'fear%20of%20competition'%20ingrained%20in%20'nativists'%20fails%20to%20consider%20America's%20lack%20of%20skilled%20manpower%20requirements.%20In%20the%20old%20days%2C%20America%20required%20immigrant%20labourers%20to%20work%20in%20its%20factories.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20country%20now%20requires%20qualified%20immigrant%20engineers%20to%20power%20the%20country's%20technology%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20research%20by%20Boundless%2C%20an%20immigration%20consultancy%2C%20points%20out%20that%20about%2073%25%20of%20the%20H-1B%20visas%20were%20issued%20to%20Indians%20compared%20to%20only%2012%25%20to%20Chinese.%20It%20shows%20the%20skills%2C%20talent%20and%20academic%20qualifications%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20are%20increasingly%20required%20over%20the%20years%20to%20shape%20America's%20primacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Indians%20form%20merely%201.5%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%2C%20they%20occupy%20high%20profile%20posts%20such%20as%20doctors%2C%20CEOs%2C%20scientists%20and%20even%20astronauts%2C%20and%20have%20the%20highest%20median%20income%20compared%20to%20other%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20feeling%20threatened%20by%20DOGE%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20Sriram%20seems%20to%20be%20far-fetched%20now.%20They%20are%20merely%20advisors%20who%20will%20probably%20help%20make%20policies.%20They%20won't%20be%20running%20the%20government%3B%20they%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndians%20living%20illegally%20in%20the%20US%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20must%20be%20tackled%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20The%20Indian%20government%20must%20take%20up%20the%20recent%20hate-mongering%20against%20Indians%20by%20MAGA%20supporters%20with%20the%20US%20government.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20stop%20all%20illegal%20migrat