folio-unbalanced-index-growth-value-investing-blackrock-inflation-diversification-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBlackRock%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20asset%20manager%2C%20recently%20suggested%20a%20bitcoin%20allocation%20within%20a%20multi-asset%20portfolio.%20It%20seemed%20to%20me%20that%20bitcoin%20had%20gained%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20legitimacy%20as%20an%20asset%20class.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20way%20to%20determine%20if%20bitcoin%20was%20really%20the%20next%20big%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20or%20if%20Wall%20Street%20simply%20had%20FOMO%20%E2%80%94%20than%20by%20buying%20bitcoin%20firsthand.%20I%20asked%20three%20financial%20experts%20for%20some%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-buy-bitcoin-price-start-investing-wall-street-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estart%20investing%20in%20bitcoin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf2ac3a6-ef0e-497d-9320-e95531619993%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20too%20late%20to%20buy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20taking%20the%20plunge%2C%20I%20had%20some%20concerns.%20Namely%2C%20was%20it%20a%20smart%20choice%20to%20buy%20after%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin%20had%20already%20run%20up%20so%20much%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJohn%20Haar%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20bitcoin%20services%20firm%20Swan%20Bitcoin%2C%20gave%20me%20an%20analogy%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20said%20'Am%20I%20too%20late%20to%20bitcoin%3F'%20my%20answer%20would%20be%20'Do%20you%20think%20you're%20too%20late%20to%20buying%20real%20estate%20or%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%3F'%20If%20an%20asset%20is%20a%20good%20storer%20of%20value%2C%20then%20it's%20going%20to%20appreciate%20over%20time%20and%20there%20isn't%20really%20a%20concept%20of%20being%20too%20late%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20at%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20I%20lamented%20my%20lack%20of%20foresight%20in%20not%20having%20stocked%20up%20in%202010%2C%20when%20it%20was%20trading%20at%20mere%20cents%20(never%20mind%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20was%20nine%20years%20old).%20But%20as%20they%20say%2C%20the%20second%20best%20time%20is%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaar%20suggested%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fdollar-cost-averaging%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDollar%252Dcost%2520averaging%2520is%2520an%2Cintervals%2520over%2520a%2520long%2520period.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edollar%20cost%20averaging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20way%20to%20build%20up%20my%20bitcoin%20investment.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20time%20the%20market%20to%20buy%20a%20dip%2C%20I%20could%20spend%20half%20of%20a%20predetermined%20allocation%20to%20bitcoin%20for%20an%20initial%20purchase.%20Then%2C%20I%20could%20slowly%20spend%20the%20other%20half%20of%20the%20money%20by%20buying%20at%20regular%20intervals.%20By%20not%20investing%20in%20a%20lump%20sum%2C%20I%20would%20still%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20future%20price%20drops%2C%20Haar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-gains-lock-in-avoid-crash-dogecoin-millionaire-bitcoin-price-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERobert%20Cannon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20financial%20advisor%20at%20Experity%20Wealth%2C%20echoed%20similar%20sentiments%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20believe%20in%20the%20future%20potential%20and%20the%20long-term%20view%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20dollar%20cost%20averaging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEssentially%2C%20if%20you're%20thinking%20about%20buying%20and%20holding%20bitcoin%20long-term%20like%20I%20was%2C%20the%20exact%20timing%20of%20when%20you%20buy%20into%20bitcoin%20is%20less%20important%20than%20simply%20just%20buying%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3fe5f8f-6c21-48f0-94bb-2f749500bc3e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDetermining%20a%20portfolio%20weight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20wondered%20how%20much%20of%20my%20portfolio%20I%20should%20allocate%20to%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDavid%20Laut%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Abound%20Financial%2C%20told%20me%20that%20he%20recommends%20his%20clients%20keep%20a%205%25%20allocation%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20gold%20and%20bitcoin%20if%20they're%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20aggressive%20investing%20style.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20because%20these%20assets%20aren't%20typically%20correlated%20with%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20to%20gold%2C%20Cannon%20has%20seen%20people%20use%20bitcoin%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestments-to-beat-rising-inflation-next-decade-investing-strategy-ubs-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einflation%20hedge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20their%20portfolios.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUltimately%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20your%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20Cannon%20told%20me.%20He's%20advised%20clients%20with%20anything%20between%201-10%25%20of%20their%20portfolio%20in%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d9c0826-2a72-4572-b438-2a5ae5e2ce14%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifferent%20ways%20to%20invest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20actually%20buying%20bitcoin%2C%20I%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20options.%20I%20could%20purchase%20the%20cryptocurrency%20directly%20on%20either%20a%20centralized%20or%20decentralized%20exchange%2C%20through%20an%20ETF%2C%20o