e%20not%20my%20goal.%20I%20believe%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lapse%2C%20maybe%20on%20my%20part%20while%20filing%20for%20the%20nomination%20which%20is%20being%20corrected.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20award%20I%20shall%20remain%20motivated%20to%20win%20more%20medals%20for%20my%20country.%20It%20is%20a%20request%20to%20everyone%2C%20please%20do%20not%20speculate%20on%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20Bhaker%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MessageBody%5C%22%3EThe%2022-year-old%20Bhaker%20became%20independent%20India's%20first%20athlete%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20Olympics%20with%20her%20bronze-winning%20show%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20individual%20and%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20events%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20Games%2C%20Harmanpreet%20led%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20to%20its%20second%20consecutive%20bronze%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20Gukesh%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20became%20the%20youngest%20ever%20World%20champion%20while%20also%20helping%20the%20Indian%20team%20win%20a%20historic%20gold%20in%20the%20Chess%20Olympiad%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20recipient%20will%20be%20para%20high-jumper%20Praveen%2C%20who%20was%20crowned%20the%20T64%20champion%20in%20the%20Paris%20Paralympics.%20The%20T64%20classification%20is%20for%20athletes%20who%20have%20one%20or%20both%20legs%20missing%20below%20the%20knee%20and%20rely%20on%20a%20prosthetic%20leg%20for%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20awardees%20will%20receive%20their%20awards%20from%20the%20President%20of%20India%20at%20a%20specially%20organised%20function%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20on%2017th%20January%2C%202025%20(Friday)%20at%201100%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sports%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735811280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fc3mrrqco_manu-bhaker_640x480_24_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fothersports%2Fmanu-bhaker-d-gukesh-among-four-athletes-to-get-dhyan-chand-khel-ratna-award-sports-ministry-7383271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Men's%20hockey%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20and%20Paralympic%20gold%20medal%20winner%20Praveen%20Kumar%20will%20also%20get%20the%20prestigious%20award%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fothersports%2Fmanu-bhaker-d-gukesh-among-four-athletes-to-get-dhyan-chand-khel-ratna-award-sports-ministry-7383271%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lalu%20Yadav%20Says%20Doors%20Open%20For%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20How%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Reacted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Thursday%20offered%20a%20cryptic%20response%20to%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20%26quot%3Bdoors%20open%26quot%3B%20statement%20to%20rejoin%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%20When%20questioned%20by%20journalists%20about%20Mr%20Yadav's%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20folded%20his%20hands%2C%20smiled%2C%20and%20curtly%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EKya%20bol%20rahe%20hain%20%3C%2Fem%3E(What%20are%20you%20saying%3F)%26quot%3B%20without%20elaborating%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exchange%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Mr%20Yadav's%20statement%20during%20an%20interview%2C%20where%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20doors%20are%20open%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20He%20should%20also%20unbolt%20his%20gates.%20This%20would%20facilitate%20movement%20of%20people%20from%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F