umar-led%20NDA%20government.%20He%20further%20accused%20Mr%20Kumar%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bcaptive%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20small%20group%20of%20close%20advisors%20and%20no%20longer%20capable%20of%20running%20Bihar%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20JD(U)%20leader%20Lalan%20Singh%20dismissed%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20is%20strong.%20JD(U)%20and%20BJP%20are%20united.%20People%20can%20say%20whatever%20they%20want%20-%20it%20is%20a%20free%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735810980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F98gqtg98_lalu-yadav-nitish-kumar_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-folded-hands-response-to-lalu-yadavs-doors-open-remark-7383348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Thursday%20offered%20a%20cryptic%20response%20to%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20%26quot%3Bdoors%20open%26quot%3B%20statement%20to%20rejoin%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-folded-hands-response-to-lalu-yadavs-doors-open-remark-7383348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Banks%20urge%20RBI%20to%20inject%20liquidity%20via%20foreign-exchange%20swaps%20amid%20crunch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735810691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-urge-rbi-to-inject-liquidity-via-foreign-exchange-swaps-amid-crunch-125010200500_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20higher%20financing%20costs%20are%20posing%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20RBI%20to%20support%20an%20economy%20that's%20witnessing%20a%20slowdown%20in%20manufacturing%20activities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2