rict%20Magistrates%20(DMs)%20in%20the%20state%20and%20made%20explosive%20remarks%20against%20the%20BSF%20and%20claimed%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BSF)%20torture%20women%2C%20but%20why%20haven't%20you%20protested%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20guarding%20borders%20is%20not%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20it's%20BSF%20duty.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20doesn't%20guard%20the%20border...When%20people%20enter%2C%20where%20are%20they%20going%3F%20The%20DMs%20have%20information%20on%20where%20they%20are%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20has%20the%20longest%20border%20with%20India%2C%20with%20West%20Bengal%20sharing%20a%202%2C272%20km-long%20boundary%20with%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20and%20Assam%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Meghalaya%20sharing%20the%20remaining%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20said%20she%20would%20%26quot%3Bsend%20a%20protest%20letter%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20told%20the%20Union%20Government%20many%20times%20that%20whatever%20you%20decide%20that%20is%20our%20way.%20But%20if%20I%20see%20someone%20supporting%20terror%20to%20disturb%20my%20state%2C%20then%20we%20have%20to%20protest.%20That's%20why%20we%20will%20send%20a%20protest%20letter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735810500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbptgf63_mamata-banerjee_625x300_28_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fborder-force-bsf-letting-infiltrators-enter-bengal-claims-mamata-banerjee-7383261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20is%20%26quot%3Bletting%20infiltrators%20enter%20West%20Bengal%26quot%3B%20from%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fborder-force-bsf-letting-infiltrators-enter-bengal-claims-mamata-banerjee-7383261%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22