000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fq1v460s_madras-high-court_625x300_29_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanna-university-case-anna-university-sexual-assault-case-being-politicised-madras-high-court-7382951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madras%20High%20Court%20today%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20case%20at%20Anna%20University%20is%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20politicised%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanna-university-case-anna-university-sexual-assault-case-being-politicised-madras-high-court-7382951%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20Must%20Play%20To%20Its%20Strengths%20In%202025%20-%20By%20Harsh%20V.%20Shringla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2F2akjsklo_pm-modi-departs-for-bhutan-_625x300_17_August_19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20in%202024%20stood%20at%20a%20crossroads%2C%20with%20global%20fault%20lines%20deepening%20and%20crises%20multiplying.%20Wars%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20upended%20the%20global%20order%2C%20disrupting%20energy%20markets%20and%20food%20security%2C%20while%20cascading%20challenges%20rippled%20through%20every%20region.%20The%20Indo-Pacific%20remained%20a%20theatre%20of%20contention%2C%20with%20China's%20aggressive%20manoeuvres%20destabilising%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20its%20borders%20with%20India.%20In%20Europe%2C%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%20continued%20to%20strain%20global%20energy%20supplies%20and%20exacerbated%20inflation.%20The%20Middle%20East%20witnessed%20escalating%20tensions%20with%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20which%20drew%20in%20international%20actors%20and%20deepened%20divides%20across%20the%20region.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Myanmar's%20internal%20strife%20and%20Bangladesh's%20political%20unrest%20threatened%20regional%20equilibrium%2C%20highlighting%20the%20fragility%20of%20South%20Asia's%20neighbourhood.%20These%20crises%20coupled%20with%20the%20persistent%20threat%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20rising%20inequality%20underscored%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20global%20challenges%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20coordinated%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20fraught%20environment%2C%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20demonstrated%20remarkable%20clarity%20and%20resilience.%20Balancing%20strategic%20autonomy%20with%20global%20engagement%2C%20India%20ensured%20its%20interests%20were%20safeguarded%20even%20as%20it%20contributed%20to%20stability%20beyond%20its%20borders.%20Its%20economic%20strategies%2C%20such%20as%20diversifying%20energy%20imports%20and%20fostering%20renewable%20energy%20partnerships%2C%20underscored%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20securing%20energy%20independence%20amidst%20global%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20elections%20in%202024%20added%20layers%20of%20geopolitical%20uncertainty.%20The%20return%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20US%20President%20brought%20shifts%20in%20Washington's%20foreign%20policy%20priorities.%20A%20powerful%20Trump%20presidency%20represents%20both%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%20for%20India.%20While%20his%20stated%20focus%20is%20on%20ending%20the%20two%20major%20conflicts%2C%20countering%20China%20and%20deepening%20ties%20with%20like-minded%20democracies%20aligns%20with%20India's%20goals%2C%20potential%20shifts%20in%20trade%20policies%20and%20his%20transactional%20approach%20to%20alliances%20could%20require%20India%20to%20navigate%20complexities%20with%20caution%20and%20tact.%20Furthermore%2C%20Trump's%20stricter%20immigration%20policies%2C%20such%20as%20changes%20to%20H-1B%20visa%20regulations%20and%20family-based%20immigration%20programmes%2C%20could%20significantly%20impact%20Indian%20professionals%20and%20the%20diaspora.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20bipartisan%20consensus%20on%20strengthening%20India-US%20relations%20remains%20intact%20and%20as%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20democracies%2C%20the%20partnership%20continues%20to%20evolve%20as%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20stability%20in%20an%20increasingly%20polarised%20world.%20India's%20diplomatic%20agility%20will%20be%20essential%20in%20navigating%20these%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20remarkable%20legacy%20in%20the%20G20%20under%20its%20Presidency%20is%20being%20carried%20forward%20by%20the%20successive%20presidencies%20of%20Brazil%20and%20South%20Africa.%20The%20continuation%20of%20India's%20policies%20rooted%20in%20human-centric%20globalisation%20and%20working%20for%20the%20global%20common%20good%20have%20enhanced%20its%20foreign%20policy%20imprint%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20The%20concept%20of%20Vishwa%20Mitra%20(Friend%20to%20the%20World)%20reflects%20India's%20commitment%20to%20collaboration%20for%20global%20well-being%20and%20sustainable%20development.%20From%20its%20leadership%20in%20the%20G20%20to%20its%20vaccine%20diplomacy%2C%20its%20advocacy%20for%20equitable%20access%20to%20digital%20public%20goods%20to%20its%20role%20as%20a%20first%20responder%20in%20times%20of%20need%2C%20India%20exemplifies%20the%20principles%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20shared%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20India%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20partner%20for%20addressing%20global%20challenges%2C%20fostering%20mutual%20respect%20and%20advancing%20a%20vision%20of%20a%20peaceful%20and%20equitable%20world%20order.%20His%20commitment%20to%20achieving%20peace%20through%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%20was%20borne%20out%20by%20his%20visits%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20in%20this%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnhancing%20Defence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20global%20conflicts%20of%202024%20underscored%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20robust%20defence%20capabilities.%20With%20global%20military%20spending%20at%20unprecedented%20levels%2C%20India's%20defence%20budget%20of%20%2481%20billion%20signals%20its%20commitment%20to%20national%20security.%20Amid%20rising%20tensions%2C%20India's%20focus%20on%20self-reliance%2C%20in%20critical%20sectors%20like%20defence%20manufacturing%20and%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20demonstrates%20its%20ability%20to%20innovate%20while%20meeting%20strategic%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegionally%2C%20India%20has%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20unprecedented%20challenges%20arising%20out%20of%20economic%20turmoil%20and%20great%20power%20rivalry%20in%20our%20immediate%20region.%20In%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20Maldives%2C%20it%20extended%20financial%20and%20technical%20support%20to%20stabilise%20economies%2C%20while%20calibrated%20diplomacy%20ensured%20continued%20engagement%20with%20Bangladesh.%20To%20safeguard%20its%20core%20interests%20in%20Bangladesh%20amidst%20its%20political%20unrest%2C%20India%20needs%20more%20proactive%20engagement%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20further%20tested%20India's%20diplomatic%20balance%20as%20it%20safeguarded%20its%20diaspora%2C%20provided%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20called%20for%20peaceful%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategic%20Autonomy%20Is%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%202025%20approaches%2C%20India%20must%20continue%20leveraging%20its%20strengths%20while%20addressing%20emerging%20challenges.%20India's%20policy%20of%20pragmatic%20strategic%20autonomy%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20navigating%20multilateral%20platforms%20and%20addressing%20the%20complexities%20of%20emerging%20geopolitics.%20Significantly%20upping%20our%20strategic%20ties%20with%20the%20US%20is%20an%20opportunity%20afforded%20by%20Trump's%20unprecedented%20win.%20Engaging%20with%20trusted%20partners%20and%20those%20not%20so%20trusted%2C%20alike%2C%20is%20necessary%20if%20we%20are%20to%20secure%20our%20larger%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeopolitically%2C%20tactfully%20managing%20China's%20assertiveness%20and%20ensuring%20regional%20stability%20will%20demand%20sustained%20engagement%20with%20Quad%20partners%20and%20in%20multilateral%20forums%20like%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO.%20Any%20rapprochement%20with%20China%20would%20need%20to%20be%20calibrated%20on%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20foreign%20policy%20will%20also%20need%20to%20continue%20to%20follow%20its%20%E2%80%98neighbourhood%20first'%20approach.%20Managing%20relations%20with%20our%20immediate%20neighbours%20will%20not%20only%20secure%20our%20vital%20national%20interests%20but%20allow%20us%20to%20deal%20with%20our%20major%20interlocutors%20more%20effectively.%20Extending%20PM%20Modi's%20most%20vision%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E'%20in%20our%20immediate%20neighbourhood%20will%20ensure%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98sabka%20vishwas'%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20India%20can%20further%20leverage%20its%20G20%20legacy%20to%20champion%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20particularly%20in%20debt%20relief%20and%20climate%20financing.%20India%20must%20continue%20its%20support%20for%20Africa%20and%20countries%20in%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20including%20by%20extending%20critical%20assistance%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20healthcare%20and%20renewable%20energy.%20Expanding%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20as%20a%20global%20public%20good%20will%20not%20only%20elevate%20India's%20technological%20leadership%20but