0got%20a%20back%20issue.%20That's%20the%20only%20injury%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%2C%20leading%20the%20series%202-1%2C%20will%20aim%20to%20secure%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20in%20Sydney%20with%20a%20refreshed%20lineup%2C%20while%20India%20remain%20focused%20on%20retaining%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20must%20win%20the%20Sydney%20Test%20match%20to%20keep%20their%20slim%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20hopes%20alive%2C%20and%20would%20also%20need%20Australia%20to%20not%20win%20either%20of%20their%20two%20Test%20matches%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20lock%20in%20their%20spot%20at%20Lord's%20summit%20clash%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20begins%20on%20Friday%20at%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735803960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Flbueuah_kohli-bumrah-twitter_650x400_01_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fnot-virat-kohli-jasprit-bumrah-video-sparks-rumour-of-25-year-old-replacing-rohit-sharma-as-india-captain-in-sydney-7382755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20asked%20if%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20designated%20India%20captain%2C%20will%20play%20in%20Sydney%20or%20not%2C%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20gave%20a%20strange%20reply%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fnot-virat-kohli-jasprit-bumrah-video-sparks-rumour-of-25-year-old-replacing-rohit-sharma-as-india-captain-in-sydney-7382755%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20New%20Orleans%20Residents%20Are%20Trading%20Guns%20for%20PlayStations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20deadly%20pickup%20truck%20attack%2C%20residents%20of%20New%20Orleans%20participated%20in%20a%20city-supported%20gun%20buyback%20initiative%20meant%20to%20improve%20public%20safety%20amid%20Louisiana's%20loosened%20gun%20ownership%20laws.%20The%20event%2C%20organized%20by%20a%20local%20nonprofit%2C%20saw%20dozens%20of%20individuals%20exchanging%20guns%20for%20gaming%20devices%2C%20with%20no%20questions%20asked%20as%20long%20the%20firearms%20were%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20two%20hours%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20city%20police%20officers%20received%20and%20dismantled%2032%20revolvers%2C%20shotguns%20and%20semi-automatics%2C%20all%20traded%20in%20exchange%20for%20gaming%20consoles%2C%20such%20as%20the%20PlayStation%205%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20participants%20was%20Leticia%20Clanton%2C%2050%2C%20who%20chose%20to%20swap%20her%20weapon%20for%20a%20PlayStation%205%20worth%20about%20%24500.%20While%20Ms%20Clanton%20had%20a%20permit%20to%20carry%20a%20concealed%20handgun%20she%20had%20owned%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20she%20also%20has%20eight%20young%20grandchildren%20running%20around%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20all%20the%20grandkids%20and%20all%20the%20violence%20that%20they%20got%20going%20on%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20get%20it%20up%20off%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20Clanton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20PlayStation%3F%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20for%20all%20of%20them%20to%20share%20when%20they%20come%20to%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Games%20For%20Guns'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20the%20city%20has%20reportedly%20collected%2094%20guns%20through%20three%20such%20buyback%20programmes.%20A%20local%20nonprofit%20called%20Unchained%20Realities%20is%20organizing%20these%20exchanges%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Nola%20Grown%20gaming%20program%20that%20engages%20young%20people%20in%20the%20city%20with%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20AP%20report%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20has%20set%20up%20two%20centres%20for%20youth%20to%20build%20skills%20and%20open%20up%20pathways%20to%20the%20gaming%20world%20%C2%A0--%20whether%20as%20a%20competitive%20player%20or%20through%20game%20development%2C%20graphic%20design%20and%20coding.%20A%20third%20centre%20is%20reportedly%20in%20the%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20my%20inbox%20is%20filled%20up%20with%20people%20who%20say%20they%20want%20to%20do%20this%2C%20I%20just%20felt%20a%20necessity%20to%20go%20out%20and%20try%20to%20raise%20some%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20JD%20Carrere%2C%20co-director%20of%20the%20gaming%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELouisiana%20Gun%20Ownership%20Laws%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Buybacks%20came%20in%20response%20to%20Louisiana's%20more%20relaxed%20gun%20ownership%20restrictions%20and%20harsher%20sentencing%20for%20violent%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Orleans%20has%20historically%20had%20one%20of%20America's%20highest%20homicide%20rates.%20However%2C%20murders%20and%20non-fatal%20shootings%20have%20decreased%20significantly%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Police%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Louisiana%20has%20toughened%20its%20laws%20for%20violent%20crimes.%20Shortly%20after%20taking%20office%20in%202024%2C%20Republican%20Governor%20Jeff%20Landry%20pushed%20a%20tough-on-crime%20agenda%20and%20brought%20laws%20to%20curb%20crime%20in%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20(GOP)%20dominated%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20laws%20passed%20is%20one%20mandating%2017-year-olds%20be%20charged%20as%20adults.%20Another%20law%20requires%20anyone%20convicted%20of%20a%20crime%20to%20serve%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20sentence%20before%20they%20can%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20also%20eased%20the%20gun%20ownership%20restrictions.%20As%20per%20a%20law%20which%20went%20into%20effect%20in%20August%2C%20most%20people%2018%20years%20or%20older%20can%20carry%20a%20concealed%20weapon%20without%20a%20government%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETruck%20Attack%20In%20New%20Orleans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20fifteen%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20of%20others%20were%20injured%20after%20US%20Army%20veteran%20Jabbar%20swerved%20around%20makeshift%20barriers%20and%20barreled%20into%20revellers%20in%20New%20Orleans'%20crowded%20French%20Quarter%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day.%20Police%20officials%20said%2042-year-old%20Jabbar%20may%20have%20had%20the%20help%20of%20others%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack%2C%20as%20three%20improvised%20pipe%20bombs%20were%20found%20nearby%20in%20the%20tourist-drawing%20French%20Quarter%2C%20including%20one%20in%20Jabbar's%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20around%203%3A15%20am%20near%20the%20intersection%20of%20Canal%20and%20Bourbon%20Streets%2C%20a%20historic%20tourist%20destination%20known%20for%20its%20music%20and%20bars%20where%20crowds%20were%20celebrating%20the%20New%20Year.%20The%20suspect%20drove%20a%20white%20Ford%20F-150%20electric%20pickup%20into%20a%20group%20of%20pedestrians%2C%20then%20exited%20and%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20shootout%20with%20police%20--%20two%20of%20whom%20were%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735803960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9ersa78o_gun-buyback-twitter_625x300_02_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-new-orleans-residents-are-trading-guns-for-playstations-7382700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20before%20the%20deadly%20pickup%20truck%20attack%2C%20residents%20of%20New%20Orleans%20participated%20in%20a%20city-supported%20gun%20buyback%20initiative%20meant%20to%20improve%20public%20safety%20as%20Louisiana%20loosened%20gun%20ownership%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-new-orleans-residents-are-trading-guns-for-pla