%20business%20backgrounds%2C%20both%20Punit%20and%20Chandni%20had%20little%20experience%20in%20product%20design%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20or%20working%20directly%20with%20artisans.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20a%20year%20to%20figure%20out%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Punit.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20sourcing%20the%20wood%20to%20finding%20the%20right%20artisans%2C%20to%20building%20the%20design%20and%20the%20brand%20itself.%20While%20it%20only%20took%20five%20minutes%20for%20me%20to%20get%20inspired%2C%20it%20was%20a%20completely%20new%20avenue%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20made%20the%20strategic%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20an%20online%2C%20Direct-to-Consumer%20(D2C)%20model%2C%20avoiding%20the%20traditional%20retail%20route.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20particular%20about%20creating%20an%20online%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punit%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20go%20into%20retail%2C%20because%20I%20believe%20the%20future%20is%20online%20businesses.%20People%20expect%20convenience%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20D2C%20offers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20launching%20an%20online%20business%20brought%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20ecosystem%20was%20complex%20and%20overwhelming%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punit%20admits%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20everything%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20early%20struggles%2C%20the%20first%20collection%20of%20Aurum%20Crafts%20was%20launched%20in%202022.%20The%20brand%E2%80%99s%20kitchenware%20%E2%80%94%20wooden%20cheese%20platters%2C%20serving%20trays%2C%20and%20cutting%20boards%20%E2%80%94%20were%20an%20instant%20hit.%20Yet%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20products%20that%20won%20over%20customers%2C%20it%20was%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20brand%20and%20the%20artisans%20who%20brought%20it%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20artists%20of%20Aurum%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20worked%20closely%20with%20several%20talented%20artisans%20from%20the%20Bagru%20region.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20production%20house%20was%20to%20see%20exactly%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20make%20these%20products%2C%20so%20I%20could%20translate%20it%20for%20our%20viewers%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandni%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20I%20spoke%20to%20one%20of%20our%20women%20painters.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380268%2Findiegood-sneha-baghrecha-sustainable-eco-friendly-pet-products-india-collaborations-animal-welfare-artisan-crafts-yoda-pfa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerational%20craftsperson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20our%20team%20had%20trained%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20spoke%20to%20me%20about%20how%20it%20was%20only%20after%20the%20passing%20of%20her%20husband%20that%20she%20had%20to%20take%20on%20a%20job%2C%20and%20by%20luck%20she%20came%20across%20our%20brand%20and%20was%20able%20to%20learn%20something%20new%20and%20run%20her%20household%20independently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-2.50.45-PM-1-1735585670.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Traditional%20craftswomen%2C%20holding%20wooden%20kitchenware%20mid%20production%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe