g%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-389010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPawsitivity%20aims%20to%20provide%20affordable%2C%20QR-enabled%20reflective%20collars%20to%20animal%20caretakers%2C%20easing%20their%20financial%20burden%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Tank%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20Animal%20Welfare%20Officer%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20speaks%20out%20of%20her%20own%20experience%20of%20working%20in%20the%20field.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20that%20during%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20firecrackers%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20panic%20and%20disorientation%20in%20dogs.%20So%20these%20QR%20collars%20really%20help%20in%20reconnecting%20the%20lost%20animals%20to%20their%20caretakers%20or%20NGOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%E2%80%99s%20group%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20relies%20heavily%20on%20these%20collars%2C%20as%20they%20are%20a%20lifesaver%20on%20highways.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20them%2C%20many%20dogs%20would%20be%20invisible%20to%20drivers%2C%20and%20accidents%20are%20inevitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20the%20animal%20welfare%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETushar%20Shende%20(39)%2C%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20has%20been%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20Pawsitivity%20journey%2C%20handling%20the%20administrative%20and%20operational%20aspects%20of%20the%20venture%20along%20with%20his%20own%20job.%20Tushar%2C%20who%20was%20once%20terrified%20of%20dogs%2C%20now%20understands%20their%20needs%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20responsible%20feeding%20and%20animal%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20both%20have%20been%20conducting%20school%20awareness%20programmes%20to%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20approach%20stray%20dogs%20and%20behave%20around%20them.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lack%20of%20understanding%20can%20lead%20to%20either%20the%20children%20hurting%20the%20animal%20or%20getting%20hurt%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20and%20respectfully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F379789%2Fkind-hour-foundation-mouli-mehrotra-lucknow-art-education-animal-welfare-compassion-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteract%20with%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creating%20positive%20experiences%20for%20both%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20programmes%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20Pawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20ensuring%20that%20children%20grow%20up%20with%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20street%20animals%20and%20a%20greater%20sense%20of%20empathy%20towards%20them.%20With%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20connections%20as%20a%20former%20teacher%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20access%20various%20schools%20and%20run%20workshops%20that%20sensitise%20young%20minds%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rimjhim%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20including%20financial%20difficulties%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20their%20passion%20for%20animal%20welfare%20has%20never%20faltered.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20pregnant%20during%20COVID%2C%20things%20were%20especially%20difficul