%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20Banjara%20tribe%20(a%20nomadic%20group%20that%20traditionally%20worked%20as%20traders%20of%20goods%20and%20cattle)%2C%20Paras%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20gnawing%20sense%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98us%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98them%E2%80%99%20divide.%20He%20saw%20the%20struggles%20faced%20by%20his%20people%20%E2%80%94%20discrimination%2C%20marginalisation%2C%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20basic%20rights%2C%20and%20most%20significantly%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20identity%20in%20a%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%2C%20like%20many%20others%20from%20the%20Banjara%20community%2C%20lived%20a%20life%20on%20the%20move%2C%20travelling%20and%20trading%20goods.%20His%20parents%20lived%20a%20nomadic%20existence%2C%20while%20Paras%E2%80%99s%20eight%20older%20siblings%20never%20even%20attended%20school%20due%20to%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20constant%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20grandfather%20would%20sell%20salt%2C%20that%20used%20to%20be%20our%20trade.%20They%20also%20used%20to%20sell%20cattle%20to%20farmers%20who%20needed%20them%20for%20agriculture.%20At%20cattle%20fairs%20organised%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20they%20would%20buy%20and%20take%20the%20cattle%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20mainly%20to%20the%20southern%20regions.%20There%2C%20tribal%20farmers%20rely%20on%20cattle%20for%20farming%20instead%20of%20using%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20transportation%20methods%20improved%20and%20small%20markets%20began%20setting%20up%2C%20this%20line%20of%20business%20became%20obsolete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20then%20had%20to%20look%20for%20other%20ways%20of%20earning.%20With%20few%20options%20available%2C%20they%20shifted%20to%20labour%20work%20and%20formed%20a%20small%20community%20of%20labourers%20where%20everyone%20would%20work%20together.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20they%20decided%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20settle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paras%20Banjara%20addressing%20a%20Jan%20Sunwai%20to%20empower%20nomadic%20communities%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20their%20voices%20on%20important%20issues.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390971%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParas%20Banjara%20addressing%20a%20Jan%20Sunwai%20to%20empower%20nomadic%20communities%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20their%20voices%20on%20important%20issues%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParas%20was%2012%20years%20old.%20Soon%20he%20would%20be%20introduced%20to%20a%20school%2C%20an%20experience%20he%20found%20to%20be%20vastly%20different%20from%20the%20open%2C%20unbound%20life%20he%20had%20known.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20kids%20in%20the%20village%20that%20we%20had%20settled%20outside%20of%2C%20would%20go%20to%20school%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99d%20accompany%20them.%20There%20were%20a%20few%20teachers%20who%20were%20really%20dedicated%3B%20if%20they%20saw%20a%20child%20in%20the%20village%20who%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20attending%20school%2C%20they%20would%20come%20to%20their%20home%20and%20take%20us%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20did%20not%20like%20it%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20cultural%20shock%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20used%20to%20wait%20outside%20all%20day%2C%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20was%20at%20ease%2C%20and%20I%20could%20concentrate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20had%20hardly%20interacted%20with%20people%20outside%20of%20his%20community%2C%20Paras%20had%20to%20constantly%20fight%20a%20feeling%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20go%20to%20school%2C%20but%20because%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20to%20anyone%20as%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20language%2C%20and%20because%20the%20children%20also%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20me%20because%20of%20my%20background%2C%20it%20was%20overwhelming.%20I%20ended%20up%20skipping%20school%20for%20many%20days%20out%20of%20fear%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20poverty%20to%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Paras%20graduated%20high%20school%2C%20his%20early%20experiences%20had%20shaped%20his%20understanding%20of%20social%20inequality%20and%20injustice.%20Whether%20it%20was%20watching%20his%20parents%20struggle%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20financial%20resources%2C%20being%20unable%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20authorities%20about%20their%20issues%2C%20or%20being%20at%20the%20epicenter%20of%20the%20problems%20his%20community%20faced%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20education%20became%20a%20crucial%20tool%20for%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20lack%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20poverty.%20My%20parents%20spent%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20help%20me%20finish%20my%20education.%20When%20you%20grow%20up%20like%20this%2C%20by%20the%20time%20you%20finish%20studying%2C%20your%20one%20and%20only%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20a%20job%20that%20gives%20you%20security%20and%20a%20place%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20admits.%20But%20right%20after%20school%2C%20he%20found%20out%20about%20%3Cem%3EMazdoor%20Kisan%20Shakti%20Sangathan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(MKSS)%2C%20a%20prominent%20organisation%20that%20demands%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20fair%20wages%20for%20workers%2C%20and%20while%20the%20need%20for%20a%20well-%20positioned%20job%20was%20ever%20present%2C%20Paras%20decided%20to%20commit%20to%20what%20he%20believed%20in%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20hardships%20that%20might%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20organisation%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20meagre%20Rs%202%2C190%20per%20month%2C%20the%20same%20as%20everyone%20else.%20Given%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20time%2C%20his%20family%20was%20skeptical%20about%20how%20this%20would%20work%20out%20practically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20quite%20difficult%20to%20convince%20my%20family%2C%20espec