977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20with%20MKSS%20for%20years%20and%20studying%20social%20work%2C%20Paras%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20pressing%20issues%20and%20mobilise%20people%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20He%20focused%20on%20creating%20small%2C%20tight-knit%20communities%20within%20larger%20communities%2C%20where%20those%20who%20could%2C%20would%20support%20others%20and%20work%20together%20to%20address%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20common%20concerns%20that%20emerged%20was%20how%20to%20secure%20these%20documents%20for%20nomadic%20people.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20struggled%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20beginning%20with%20how%20to%20make%20these%20issues%20visible%2C%20understandable%2C%20and%20addressable%20to%20all%20stakeholders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20shares.%20Something%20as%20simple%20as%20getting%20a%20caste%20certificate%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20difficult%20and%20confusing%20process%20for%20many%2C%20including%20the%20lower-level%20government%20officials%20in%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20some%20places%2C%20the%20lower%20bureaucracy%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20proactive%20and%20willing%20to%20help%2C%20others%20found%20themselves%20stuck%20in%20the%20process%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20the%20social%20structure%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262912%2Fdalit-woman-inspires-girl-child-education-uttar-pradesh-skvs-founder%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaste%20sy