0of%20nomadic%20communities.%20He%20worked%20with%20both%20major%20political%20parties%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20include%20these%20issues%20in%20their%20electoral%20manifestos.%20To%20ensure%20a%20thorough%20understanding%2C%20Paras%20and%20his%20team%20also%20prepared%20their%20own%20charters%20and%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Suchna%20Evum%20Rozgar%20Adhikar%20Abhiyan%20(SR.%20Abhiyan)%20to%20draft%20a%20manifesto%20specifically%20for%20nomads.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20we%20vote%20for%20you%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20recognize%20our%20struggles%3F%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20emphasises.%20To%20hold%20politicians%20accountable%2C%20they%20organise%20Jan%20Manch%20events%2C%20where%20they%20question%20leaders%20on%20their%20commitment%20to%20addressing%20nomadic%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20community%20has%20a%20rightful%20claim%20to%20at%20least%20450%20square%20feet%20of%20land%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20by%20actively%20engaging%20all%20touchpoints%20of%20the%20socio-political%20spectrum%2C%20we%20can%20bring%20out%20real%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%3A%20Paras%20Banjara%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735183800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D390926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%20twenty%20years%2C%20Paras%20Banjara%2C%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20fighting%20discrimination%2C%20securing%20vital%20documents%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20land%20ownership%20for%20Rajasthan's%20nomadic%20tribes.%20Through%20Olakhaan%20Trust%2C%20he%20aims%20to%20reclaim%20their%20lost%20identity%20and%20ensure%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society%2C%20giving%20nomadic%20voices%20the%20recognition%20and%20rights%20they%20deserve.%22%2C%22author%22%3A